---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="FridgeMenu - AI Recipe Chef" description="Cook what you already have. Enter ingredients, get recipes, step-by-step cooking mode with voice. Free.">
  <div class="pt-24 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
      <a href="/en/apps" class="text-sm text-text-muted hover:text-accent-purple transition-colors">&larr; All apps</a>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-6 mt-8 mb-12">
        <img src="/apps/ghostkitchen-icon.png" alt="FridgeMenu icon" width="128" height="128" class="rounded-[28px] shadow-lg" />
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-3"><span class="gradient-text">FridgeMenu</span></h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-text-muted">Cook What You Already Have</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card-hover p-8 rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card mb-8">
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Open the fridge, type what you see, and FridgeMenu turns it into dinner. AI finds the best recipes from your available ingredients, then guides you step by step — hands-free with voice commands.
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          No more staring at the fridge thinking "there's nothing to eat." You have chicken, rice, and an onion? That's a recipe. FridgeMenu matches your ingredients to 40 curated recipes and walks you through cooking — with built-in timers so nothing burns.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Your Personal Sous Chef</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Cooking mode reads each step out loud. Hands covered in flour? Say "next" and FridgeMenu moves to the next step. Timers start automatically when the recipe says "bake for 20 minutes." It's like having a chef standing next to you.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Features</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-text-muted mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">40 Curated Recipes</strong> — real dishes that work, not AI-hallucinated combinations. Each tested and balanced</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Voice Commands</strong> — say "next", "repeat", or "timer" while cooking. No need to touch the screen with messy hands</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Built-in Timers</strong> — automatic timers for every step that needs one. Multiple timers running simultaneously</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Dietary Preferences</strong> — vegetarian, gluten-free, dairy-free — set your preferences and see only recipes that fit</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Cooking History</strong> — track what you've made, rate your favorites, build your personal cookbook over time</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-accent-green mt-1">&#10003;</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Works Offline</strong> — all recipes stored on device. No internet needed once installed. Cook anywhere</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card-hover p-8 rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Coming to App Store</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted">FridgeMenu is preparing for release. Free for iOS.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-hover p-8 rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Privacy</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted mb-3">Everything runs on your device. No ingredient lists, no recipes, no cooking data is sent anywhere. Your kitchen stays yours.</p>
        <a href="/apps/ghostkitchen/privacy" class="text-sm text-accent-purple hover:underline">Privacy Policy &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <div class="text-sm text-text-muted">
        <p>Questions or feedback: <a href="mailto:magic4e@gmail.com" class="text-accent-purple hover:underline">magic4e@gmail.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
